{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1679-02_129", "resp": "mercure"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Madrigal"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", février 1679 [tome 2], p. 129-131."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "On croit quelquefois ne donner son cœur qu’en riant. Il est reçeu de la mesme sorte. On s’accoûtume à se voir, & l’habitude estant une fois formée, il n’y a plus moyen de s’en dédire. C’est ce que vous trouverez fort spirituellement décrit dans ce Madrigal. Il est de M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[2]", "text": " le Chevalier de la Terrie, Capitaine au Regiment du Roy, & fait voir que le commerce des Muses n’est pas incompatible avec la profession des Armes."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Madrigal."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[1]/seg[1]", "tag": "seg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[1]/seg[1]/text()[1]", "text": "    "}], "attributes": {"type": "tab"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Une simple inclination"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Dans ses commencemens est toûjours peu de chose."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Un cœur sur sa fierté bien souvent se repose,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[4]/seg[1]", "tag": "seg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[4]/seg[1]/text()[1]", "text": "    "}], "attributes": {"type": "tab"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Sans crainte & sans précaution."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[5]/seg[1]", "tag": "seg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[5]/seg[1]/text()[1]", "text": "    "}], "attributes": {"type": "tab"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais ce panchant si doux en apparence,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[6]/seg[1]", "tag": "seg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[6]/seg[1]/text()[1]", "text": "    "}], "attributes": {"type": "tab"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "Va bientost plus loin qu’on ne pense,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": "Sans qu’on s’en apperçoive, on se laisse enflâmer,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": "On soufre avec plaisir un mouvement si tendre,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[9]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[9]/text()[1]", "text": "Et quand ce cœur surpris commence à s’alarmer,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[10]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[10]/seg[1]", "tag": "seg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[10]/seg[1]/text()[1]", "text": "    "}], "attributes": {"type": "tab"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[10]/text()[1]", "text": "Il n’est plus temps de se défendre."}]}], "attributes": {"rend": "border"}}]}